languages.text: "То мне неведомо. Однако от моего взора не укрылся его интерес к тебе, элантах. Будь осторож{mf|ен|на} — внимание Аребенниан не сулит ничего хорошего. Многие считают, что заговорить с ним уже равносильно смертному приговору".

traits.locale_text: "То мне неведомо. Однако от моего взора не укрылся его интерес к тебе, элантах. Будь осторож{mf|ен|на} — внимание Аребенниан не сулит ничего хорошего. Многие считают, что заговорить с ним уже равносильно смертному приговору".
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: "That I do not know. But what is not hidden from my gaze is his interest in you, elantach. Tread carefully — attention from an Arebennian bodes nothing good. Many believe that even speaking to one is tantamount to a death sentence."

languages.text: “这我就不知道了，但很明显，他对你非常感兴趣，外界人。一定要谨慎行事，因为来自独角的关注通常都不是什么好兆头。很多人认为，哪怕仅仅是和独角说过话，就等同于被判了死刑。”
languages.original_text: "That I do not know. But what is not hidden from my gaze is his interest in you, elantach. Tread carefully — attention from an Arebennian bodes nothing good. Many believe that even speaking to one is tantamount to a death sentence."

traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: «Eso lo desconozco. Sin embargo, lo que no se oculta a mi mirada es su interés por ti, elantach. Ten cuidado: la atención de un Arebennian no augura nada bueno. Muchos creen que hablar con uno de ellos es una condena a muerte».
languages.original_text: "That I do not know. But what is not hidden from my gaze is his interest in you, elantach. Tread carefully — attention from an Arebennian bodes nothing good. Many believe that even speaking to one is tantamount to a death sentence."

languages.text: 「それはわからない。しかし、彼は明らかに陛下に興味を示している、エランタ。用心したほうがいい。アーベニアンの気を引いてしまうとろくなことがない。彼らと話すことさえ死刑宣告に等しいと考える者も多い」
languages.original_text: "That I do not know. But what is not hidden from my gaze is his interest in you, elantach. Tread carefully — attention from an Arebennian bodes nothing good. Many believe that even speaking to one is tantamount to a death sentence."

traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: "Das weiß ich nicht. Was meinem Blick jedoch nicht verborgen bleibt, Elantach, ist sein Interesse an Euch. Seid auf der Hut — die Aufmerksamkeit eines Arebennian kann nichts Gutes verheißen. Viele glauben, dass schon mit einem zu sprechen einem Todesurteil gleichkommt."
languages.original_text: "That I do not know. But what is not hidden from my gaze is his interest in you, elantach. Tread carefully — attention from an Arebennian bodes nothing good. Many believe that even speaking to one is tantamount to a death sentence."

languages.text: « Ça, je l'ignore, mais je n'ai pas pu m'empêcher de remarquer l'intérêt qu'il vous portait, elantach. Restez sur vos gardes : une telle attention n'augure rien de bon. Pour beaucoup, une simple conversation avec un Arebennian équivaut à une condamnation à mort. »
languages.original_text: "That I do not know. But what is not hidden from my gaze is his interest in you, elantach. Tread carefully — attention from an Arebennian bodes nothing good. Many believe that even speaking to one is tantamount to a death sentence."

languages.text: "İşte bunu bilmiyorum. Ancak bakışlarımdan kaçmayan, sana olan ilgisiydi elantach. Dikkatli ol. Bir Arebennian'ın ilgisini çekmek, hayra alamet değildir. Pek çokları, biriyle konuşmayı bile ölüm cezasına eş değer olarak görür."
